{"tid":324890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[過來人分享]DSE低分想入HKCC既諗清諗楚!!!","createTime":"2017-07-16T19:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T16:04:45.000Z","uid":51598,"like":17,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"524f2b4cb0944f246f74207683f6e3af8ae399b6","tid":324890,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T19:18:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">dse低分既你地入到去多數墊底！</span></span> <br />\n文科engine個d我唔清楚, 但商科既人都係勁 (特別係HS/acct呢2個programme, mkt就差d) <br />\n以我所知商科既人平均dse分數係18 19分， 20分以上大有人在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但HKCC連12 - 15既人都收, 如果你係呢個range既人 <br />\n我可以同你講, 你入到去讀多數都係墊底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係GPA唔夠人高冇UGC offer入唔到U <br />\n雖然你可以話咁未必DSE分未必等於GPA架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但以咁多年例子可以話你聽 <br />\n高gpa既多數dse分數一定唔低 起碼唔會係唔過16分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以如果你係冇17分18分入去, 你唔好咁開心以為有得讀好正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左第一個sem你知咩事架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所謂既8成升學率係用黎打飛機  <br />\n大部分人入HKCC都係因為佢升學率高<br />\n但其實實質只係3成人升到ugc 其餘都係OU, speed個類自資大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n(speed係易入但學費貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本係用黎賺錢 ) <br />\n當你唔好采gpa低, 想升學既話只會得返speed可以選擇   <br />\n一係行回頭路去retake dse/去ive讀個hd出黎做野算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\nHKCC完全冇考慮過dse 12 - 15分既人既能力夠唔夠讀到ASSO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHKCC入面競爭好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n上面都講左只有3成ugc升學, 話就話poly其實都收好多cc仔 <br />\n但最慘係cc入面多勁人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n你係咪個班勁人就唔知, 但讀書壓力大係真既 <br />\n你肯定會同我講, 怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我入到去會好努力讀努力過dse個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n講你就輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ASSO堂就上得幾個鍾, Sem break又成個月 <br />\n你考完dse仲會唔會咁有毅力落完堂就去溫書?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係落完堂返左屋企打機? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你肯定自己呢2年可以日日過住dse既日子而唔會hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncc入面仲有痴線佬可以用sem break放假既時間溫定下個sem既科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你係咪肯定自己有鬥心同呢班人爭ugc?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAsso努力同成果唔成比例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有讀到書既人可以mid term exam前一兩日先溫都拎到A返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (你自問dse係咪冇咩點溫都有18 19分?) <br />\n有努力既人要日日溫日日背先拎到A返黎 <br />\n有根本唔係讀書材料既人即使日日溫頂盡都係拎個B返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n另一個因素係睇你會唔會遇到伏lecturer <br />\n即係嚴, 少會派A grade, 多派爛grade去拉低你gpa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n仲有一旦遇到freerider你要獨自咩起成份project你就大撚獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你可能會諗 車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  死一科姐 我另一科追返咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n一個sem入面爛一科已經拉低左好多gpa <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平均cgpa(3-4個sem加埋既總gpa)要3.5 以上先有ugc offer <br />\n即係你每個sem至少要有一科A先有U入 <br />\n拎A要既努力同采數對每個人黎講都唔同(上面講左) <br />\n出唔晒下面再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffa6fcf1a95d2915e49925145b29fa06b8fc687","tid":324890,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T19:20:05.000Z","msg":"有試過背科mid term mc岩4x/50條先係mean <br />\n係你冇睇錯係mean mean只係B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (gpa 3) <br />\n你mid term唔過mean好難拎A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\nExam係會更加難 所以好難追返 <br />\n多數個科拎A+/A既人 mid term唔會只有mean水平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你努力溫既同時 你唔好唔記得 <br />\n你隔離左右前前後後都係望高gpa入返ugc <br />\n所以話個讀書壓力有幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac1c54853431de218bb7b6d4f06043bdaf23cae","tid":324890,"uid":12984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T19:22:31.000Z","msg":"上年上返Poly<br />\ndse 16分<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7aa64aefacd8cead850c2b8c896ef37a846151","tid":324890,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T19:26:42.000Z","msg":"仲有一點要提醒既 <br />\n入到cc唔好諗住正呀新環境新學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n如果你有呢個心態最後只會失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\ncc又冇hall(係根本冇可能有hall 佢收咁多學生) <br />\n你住得遠日日都會晒時間返學  <br />\nwk同hhb既位置都同地鐵站唔近 (hhb唔評論, 我返wk個邊) <br />\nwk係油麻地站同奧運站中間 <br />\n2邊都係要行10分鐘先到 <br />\n夏天又曬又熱 特別係油麻地個邊 個太陽係頭頂直射落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\ncc入面又冇canteen, 淨係得Pacific Coffee同7仔<br />\n出面既野食都唔好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n黎黎去去譚仔, 茶記, 太興, 蒸飯 (好似新開左爭鮮)<br />\n我真係數唔出仲有邊幾間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n奧海城入面個food count又貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlunch time放2個鍾先夠時間行去旺角食 <br />\n係wk讀書慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n環境差都算喇 學校設施又垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每逢mid term exam前學校拉巴都會多人到你想像唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天真既我第一日去到拉巴覺得好正好大有好多位俾人溫書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n係既呢個情況只會係開sem既week 1見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (真係好多位任坐) <br />\n最離譜係mid term exam前你想溫書都溫唔到呀! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解呀?!<br />\n原因好on9, 係一個位都搵唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吓! 咁拉巴冇位咪求其搵個位坐囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係wk mid term前你唔會搵到有空位俾你坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     <br />\n你唯一選擇係返屋企溫/坐地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (冇見過人咁做 ) <br />\n一係就冇台用, 係班房出面既位 (都未必有 ) <br />\n最嬲係 就算有位你都好難搵到一個靜既位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過係拉巴坐條路旁邊既位 <br />\nd人又唔知已經冇晒位 仲不斷入黎睇下搵下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\nd人就不斷係你身邊行黎行去 塊地板仲要震下震下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試問呢個環境點專心溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本wk本身已經好多asso學生，仲要同埋班speed既學生share學校資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249638aafd7ddf67212feaadb0da9f382a5796fd","tid":324890,"uid":12984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T19:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有一點要提醒既 <br />\n入到cc唔好諗住正呀新環境新學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n如果你有呢個心態最後只會失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\ncc又冇hall(係根本冇可能有hall 佢收咁多學生) <br />\n你住得遠日日都會晒時間返學  <br />\nwk同hhb既位置都同地鐵站唔近 (hhb唔評論, 我返wk個邊) <br />\nwk係油麻地站同奧運站中間 <br />\n2邊都係要行10分鐘先到 <br />\n夏天又曬又熱 特別係油麻地個邊 個太陽係頭頂直射落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\ncc入面又冇canteen, 淨係得Pacific Coffee同7仔<br />\n出面既野食都唔好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n黎黎去去譚仔, 茶記, 太興, 蒸飯 (好似新開左爭鮮)<br />\n我真係數唔出仲有邊幾間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n奧海城入面個food count又貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlunch time放2個鍾先夠時間行去旺角食 <br />\n係wk讀書慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n環境差都算喇 學校設施又垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每逢mid term exam前學校拉巴都會多人到你想像唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天真既我第一日去到拉巴覺得好正好大有好多位俾人溫書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n係既呢個情況只會係開sem既week 1見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (真係好多位任坐) <br />\n最離譜係mid term exam前你想溫書都溫唔到呀! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解呀?!<br />\n原因好on9, 係一個位都搵唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吓! 咁拉巴冇位咪求其搵個位坐囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係wk mid term前你唔會搵到有空位俾你坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     <br />\n你唯一選擇係返屋企溫/坐地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (冇見過人咁做 ) <br />\n一係就冇台用, 係班房出面既位 (都未必有 ) <br />\n最嬲係 就算有位你都好難搵到一個靜既位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過係拉巴坐條路旁邊既位 <br />\nd人又唔知已經冇晒位 仲不斷入黎睇下搵下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\nd人就不斷係你身邊行黎行去 塊地板仲要震下震下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試問呢個環境點專心溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本wk本身已經好多asso學生，仲要同埋班speed既學生share學校資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n橙"},{"pid":"761e1daf2fd2ded2ccb1382be6d9bd6e17118d8c","tid":324890,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T19:34:44.000Z","msg":"建議低分既你地揀CCCU好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面班人hea過HKCC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (但當然係更大機會遇到freerider)<br />\n朋友例子，佢讀左1年HKCC GPA 2.9左右，quit左因為自知唔會入得返ugc<br />\n轉左去CCCU重新讀過asso，而家year 1 gpa 3.6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDSE英文得3 入去已經lead住人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係HKCC係俾人lead住個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCCCU又可以用到城大既校園設施 (拉巴，canteen)<br />\n雖然HKCC都可以用到poly既校園設施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (但你係wk讀既話唔會咁有心機特登搭半粒鐘shuttle去poly)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d80fc219dac0200b33f28341517ff9edccccacd","tid":324890,"uid":12813,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":