" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     <br />\n你唯一選擇係返屋企溫/坐地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (冇見過人咁做 ) <br />\n一係就冇台用, 係班房出面既位 (都未必有 ) <br />\n最嬲係 就算有位你都好難搵到一個靜既位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過係拉巴坐條路旁邊既位 <br />\nd人又唔知已經冇晒位 仲不斷入黎睇下搵下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\nd人就不斷係你身邊行黎行去 塊地板仲要震下震下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試問呢個環境點專心溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本wk本身已經好多asso學生，仲要同埋班speed既學生share學校資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上左岸嘅人表示 好掛住WK環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要幫CC平反下<br />\nWK又新 廁所世界級 電腦又快 printer又快<br />\n<br />\n依加係U print份野 連等部腦load都等到2046<br />\nMid term period 成間都係人黎講<br />\n依個情況根本其他U都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCommon area黎講 CC都尚算幾多啦 起碼差唔多層層都有好多自閉位 又有大枱<br />\n<br />\n重有CC已經少左街外人白撞霸住晒學校資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好老實入到CC最緊要都係睇你心態同造化<br />\nCC的確係好多勁人 名校出身炒中文又有 DSE失手又有<br />\n不過都見過有DSE唔高分但入到CC肯勤力 入得返UGC嘅例子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9f59af0c4ea8d80c6fff8894f45c025866990c","tid":324890,"uid":77959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T20:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議低分既你地揀CCCU好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面班人hea過HKCC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (但當然係更大機會遇到freerider)<br />\n朋友例子，佢讀左1年HKCC GPA 2.9左右，quit左因為自知唔會入得返ugc<br />\n轉左去CCCU重新讀過asso，而家year 1 gpa 3.6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDSE英文得3 入去已經lead住人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係HKCC係俾人lead住個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCCCU又可以用到城大既校園設施 (拉巴，canteen)<br />\n雖然HKCC都可以用到poly既校園設施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (但你係wk讀既話唔會咁有心機特登搭半粒鐘shuttle去poly)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌CCCU啲人廢到仆街，之前有個gpmate CCCU升上嚟，同佢一組慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593af88612e70a82dddeb8e05eb271e86e95f142","tid":324890,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T21:24:25.000Z","msg":"space都一樣<br />\n<br />\n結論：低分咪讀asso<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd27cc8aff9ff505ad6ba2961ef866473728a51","tid":324890,"uid":15624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:44:43.000Z","msg":"你既結論既係 垃圾不如唔好讀 認命出黎做野/ 讀啲讀完hd/asso都做得既工/retake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"045f21be44c680f04b93d99113e3ebc5134a3670","tid":324890,"uid":78648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:50:33.000Z","msg":"人唔笑狗都吠啦，低分就唔好入hkcc,入得hkcc都係垃圾低分架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04921aa4eba4d2072f8ee31c829779bae03de985","tid":324890,"uid":77948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:11:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你既結論既係 垃圾不如唔好讀 認命出黎做野/ 讀啲讀完hd/asso都做得既工/retake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n其實無錯"},{"pid":"688495220248c365d4b9d1689dc4302e0a1dd370","tid":324890,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人唔笑狗都吠啦，低分就唔好入hkcc,入得hkcc都係垃圾低分架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb334737f41dcaef9f525cdd267ce50bded7d2bd","tid":324890,"uid":116254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">dse低分既你地入到去多數墊底！</span></span> <br />\n文科engine個d我唔清楚, 但商科既人都係勁 (特別係HS/acct呢2個programme, mkt就差d) <br />\n以我所知商科既人平均dse分數係18 19分， 20分以上大有人在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但HKCC連12 - 15既人都收, 如果你係呢個range既人 <br />\n我可以同你講, 你入到去讀多數都係墊底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係GPA唔夠人高冇UGC offer入唔到U <br />\n雖然你可以話咁未必DSE分未必等於GPA架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但以咁多年例子可以話你聽 <br />\n高gpa既多數dse分數一定唔低 起碼唔會係唔過16分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以如果你係冇17分18分入去, 你唔好咁開心以為有得讀好正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左第一個sem你知咩事架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所謂既8成升學率係用黎打飛機  <br />\n大部分人入HKCC都係因為佢升學率高<br />\n但其實實質只係3成人升到ugc 其餘都係OU, speed個類自資大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n(speed係易入但學費貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本係用黎賺錢 ) <br />\n當你唔好采gpa低, 想升學既話只會得返speed可以選擇   <br />\n一係行回頭路去retake dse/去ive讀個hd出黎做野算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\nHKCC完全冇考慮過dse 12 - 15分既人既能力夠唔夠讀到ASSO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHKCC入面競爭好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n上面都講左只有3成ugc升學, 話就話poly其實都收好多cc仔 <br />\n但最慘係cc入面多勁人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n你係咪個班勁人就唔知, 但讀書壓力大係真既 <br />\n你肯定會同我講, 怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我入到去會好努力讀努力過dse個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n講你就輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ASSO堂就上得幾個鍾, Sem break又成個月 <br />\n你考完dse仲會唔會咁有毅力落完堂就去溫書?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係落完堂返左屋企打機? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你肯定自己呢2年可以日日過住dse既日子而唔會hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncc入面仲有痴線佬可以用sem break放假既時間溫定下個sem既科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你係咪肯定自己有鬥心同呢班人爭ugc?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAsso努力同成果唔成比例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有讀到書既人可以mid term exam前一兩日先溫都拎到A返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (你自問dse係咪冇咩點溫都有18 19分?) <br />\n有努力既人要日日溫日日背先拎到A返黎 <br />\n有根本唔係讀書材料既人即使日日溫頂盡都係拎個B返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n另一個因素係睇你會唔會遇到伏lecturer <br />\n即係嚴, 少會派A grade, 多派爛grade去拉低你gpa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n仲有一旦遇到freerider你要獨自咩起成份project你就大撚獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你可能會諗 車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  死一科姐 我另一科追返咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n一個sem入面爛一科已經拉低左好多gpa <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平均cgpa(3-4個sem加埋既總gpa)要3.5 以上先有ugc offer <br />\n即係你每個sem至少要有一科A先有U入 <br />\n拎A要既努力同采數對每個人黎講都唔同(上面講左) <br />\n出唔晒下面再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知health study既人勁唔勁？"},{"pid":"e52cd0f5fe18651912999af5b36b2607781e8bb7","tid":324890,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ee9224947b7c3509235dfd519fcc552c284357","tid":324890,"uid":451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:38:16.000Z","msg":"點解cccu都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68416cf16a31a11b2965849cdc5ffde699f85f03","tid":324890,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解cccu都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係打手既我自己唔入hkcc啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2cc92a39058f33f15fca5663c41c4faa72d3b0","tid":324890,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解cccu都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係打手既我自己唔入hkcc啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主擺明倒緊米<br />\n<br />\nbtw準hkcc asso仔"},{"pid":"b43a8c521c670704b8c59553390eb7f253bd896a","tid":324890,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解cccu都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係打手既我自己唔入hkcc啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主擺明倒緊米<br />\n<br />\nbtw準hkcc asso仔</blockquote><br />\n如果你係我上面講個堆低分<br />\n可以同你講呢2年你點讀最後都係自資/speed/top up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲要year 1壓力大到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f30a0cc2a2c28a9982ec95b2f6a47c7ce05931","tid":324890,"uid":31920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解cccu都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係打手既我自己唔入hkcc啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主擺明倒緊米<br />\n<br />\nbtw準hkcc asso仔</blockquote><br />\n樓主係on9仔自己讀唔掂就懶係警世<br />\n識人DSE 15分之後收到3個UGC offer<br />\n仲有大把10幾分既收到Shitty"},{"pid":"0f5977e4ffe3f32d28985e9b3523c4a81205b96a","tid":324890,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解cccu都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係打手既我自己唔入hkcc啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主擺明倒緊米<br />\n<br />\nbtw準hkcc asso仔</blockquote><br />\n如果你係我上面講個堆低分<br />\n可以同你講呢2年你點讀最後都係自資/speed/top up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲要year 1壓力大到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好可惜勁多on9仔比佢90%升學率呃到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為9成升ugc真係得啖笑，health studies 又係年年幾百人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頭幾十個升nursing, 其他點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9ab8f8909905ac8e7fe96aaeb40276466bf728","tid":324890,"uid":48141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:08:20.000Z","msg":"On99<br />\n讀hkcc點會搵唔到地方溫書<br />\n點會冇野食<br />\nHkcc學生係可以入到poly campus library 同canteen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f965d0c31b372d565dc6005c37dfe1ad965b2f1","tid":324890,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquot