ockquote><br />\n人地講緊wk 唔係hhb 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhhb 當然自由入poly 啦10 分鐘路程，但wk 點會特登返poly 食canteen, 仲有poly 圖書館都唔會成日去掛，始終同學校有段距離"}]}